<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>应对焦虑 on 布斯行</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/</link><description>Recent content in 应对焦虑 on 布斯行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 25 Dec 2020 22:51:06 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>吼呆时刻360-即刻应对</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-25-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB360-%E5%8D%B3%E5%88%BB%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9/</link><pubDate>Fri, 25 Dec 2020 22:51:06 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-25-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB360-%E5%8D%B3%E5%88%BB%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9/</guid><description>培养积极心态，焦虑出现时以接纳的态度面对，可以让焦虑情绪自然地发生和消失。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻359-停止忧虑</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB359-%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%BF%A7%E8%99%91/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Dec 2020 22:45:29 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB359-%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%BF%A7%E8%99%91/</guid><description>当人们困在过分忧虑的漩涡中，往往会对觉察到的危险思前想后，最后整个脑海都被占据，不能自拔。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻358-简化生活</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB358-%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Dec 2020 23:03:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB358-%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/</guid><description>简单的生活就是不再去做那些只消耗时间和金钱却不能丰富人生的事情。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻357-呵护自己</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB357-%E5%91%B5%E6%8A%A4%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/</link><pubDate>Tue, 22 Dec 2020 23:24:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB357-%E5%91%B5%E6%8A%A4%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/</guid><description>花时间呵护自己，人们可以有精力、耐力沉着冷静地去做事，去实现自己的目标，去构建自己的人生。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻356-经常运动</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB356-%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 21 Dec 2020 22:56:13 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB356-%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8/</guid><description>经常运动是缓解焦虑最有效的方法之一。人感到焦虑时，身体“战或逃”反应加剧，肾上腺素激增。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻355-正视恐惧</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB355-%E6%AD%A3%E8%A7%86%E6%81%90%E6%83%A7/</link><pubDate>Sun, 20 Dec 2020 22:01:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB355-%E6%AD%A3%E8%A7%86%E6%81%90%E6%83%A7/</guid><description>克服恐惧最有效的方法就是正视恐惧，继续回避恐怖情境只会让心心念念想要消除的恐惧进一步加深。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻354-思考问题从现实出发</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB354-%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BB%8E%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Dec 2020 22:00:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB354-%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BB%8E%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91/</guid><description>与承认自己的责任相比，把个人感受归咎于其他人或其他事要容易得多，但只有愿意承认自己的责任，才能真正主宰自己的人生。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻353-放松精神</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB353-%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Dec 2020 23:10:12 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB353-%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/</guid><description>焦虑会加快大脑思考的速度，让人感觉思绪飞转，脑海中不停涌现各种想法。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻352-放松身体</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB352-%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93/</link><pubDate>Thu, 17 Dec 2020 21:51:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91/2020-12-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB352-%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93/</guid><description>焦虑存在于头脑中，存在于身体的每一处</description></item></channel></rss>